model.houm.property__published_new_prope.raw_sql:
with Published_NewProperties as (
select properties.id as property_id 
        ,properties.country
        , case when real_estate_developments_developments.development_status like 'completed' then 'EntregaInmediata' 
              when real_estate_developments_developments.development_status like 'site_plan_approved' then 'EnBlanco'           
              when real_estate_developments_developments.development_status like 'under_construction' then 'EnVerde'   
              when real_estate_developments_developments.development_status like 'proposed' then 'Planos'
              end as project_phase
        ,arriendoasegurado_propertydetails.latitud as latitude
        ,arriendoasegurado_propertydetails.longitud as longitude
        ,real_estate_developments_units.status as unit_status
        ,properties.supply_relation
      	,real_estate_developments_developmentdetails.reservation_value reservation_value
      	,real_estate_developments_developments.has_pilot
      	,real_estate_developments_developments.has_show_unit
        -- Tipologias data 
        , real_estate_developments_unittypes.id type_id
        , real_estate_developments_unittypes.name tipology
        , real_estate_developments_units.name as nombre_unidad
        , (case when properties.type = 'departamento' then 'depto 🏢' else type || ' 🏠' end)  as property_type
        , real_estate_developments_unittypes.rooms Dor
        , real_estate_developments_unittypes.bathrooms bath
        , real_estate_developments_unittypes.usable_area
        , real_estate_developments_unittypes.building_area
        -- Unidad 
        , real_estate_developments_units.currency
        , real_estate_developments_units.id unit_id 
        , arriendoasegurado_propertydetails.valor_venta as min_unit_price
        , real_estate_developments_units.price as unit_price
        , real_estate_developments_units.price/Nullif( (usable_area - building_area)*0.5+usable_area,0) m2_unit_price
        --, round(real_estate_developments_units.loan_monthly_payment/0.3) as Renta_mínima
        , real_estate_developments_units.suggested_rent as ReV
        , (real_estate_developments_units.suggested_rent*12)/real_estate_developments_units.price::double precision as Cap_rate
        --, real_estate_developments_units.suggested_rent*12 as Renta_anual
        , real_estate_developments_units.floor  as floor 
        , real_estate_developments_units.parking_spaces park
        , real_estate_developments_units.has_storage
        , properties_associationamenities.has_patio
        , properties_associationamenities.has_playground
        , properties_associationamenities.has_pet_area
        , properties_associationamenities.has_roof_garden
        , case when properties_associationamenities.has_patio
            or properties_associationamenities.has_playground
            or properties_associationamenities.has_pet_area
            or properties_associationamenities.has_roof_garden
            then true  else false end gree_area_boolean
        --, bi_orientation.orientation_esp
        , real_estate_developments_units.orientation
from {{ ref('proc_new_properties') }} properties
left join {{ ref('stg_users') }} users on users.id = properties.user_id 
left join {{ ref('proc_property_salesdetails') }} properties_salesdetails on properties_salesdetails.property_id = properties.id
left join {{ ref('proc_propertydetails') }} arriendoasegurado_propertydetails on arriendoasegurado_propertydetails.property_id = properties.id 
left join {{ ref('stg_real_estate_developments_developments') }} real_estate_developments_developments on real_estate_developments_developments.property_id = properties.id 
left join {{ ref('stg_real_estate_developments_developmentdetails') }} real_estate_developments_developmentdetails on real_estate_developments_developments.id  = real_estate_developments_developmentdetails.development_id 
left join {{ ref('stg_real_estate_developments_unittypes') }} real_estate_developments_unittypes on real_estate_developments_unittypes.development_id = real_estate_developments_developments.id
left join {{ ref('stg_real_estate_developments_units') }} real_estate_developments_units on real_estate_developments_units.unit_type_id = real_estate_developments_unittypes.id 
left join {{ ref('stg_properties_associationamenities') }} properties_associationamenities on properties_associationamenities.property_id = properties.id 
where true
and properties_salesdetails.status = 'published'
and properties.is_deleted = False  
and properties.for_sales = True
and upper(properties.country) in ('COLOMBIA','CHILE')
)

SELECT *
FROM Published_NewProperties

model.houm.property__published_propertie.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}
with valor_uf as (
    select valor from economic_indicator_uf 
    order by fecha desc
    limit 1
    )
, tabla_final as (
SELECT 
        a.id as property_id 
        ,a.created_at 
        ,a.updated_at
        ,a.country
        ,a.region 
        ,a.comuna
        ,a.type
        ,a.supply_relation
        ,a.business_type
        ,b.status as rental_status
        ,c.status as sales_status
        ,a.first_publication_date as first_rental_publication_date
        ,c.first_publication_date as first_sales_publication_date
        ,b.valor
        ,b.valor_venta
        ,b.currency_code as rentals_currency_code
        ,c.currency_code as sales_currency_code
        ,case when (a.country like 'Ch%' and b.currency_code::text like '%CLF%') then (b.valor::float*valor_uf.valor::float) else b.valor::float end "normalized_rentals_price"
        ,case when (a.country like 'Ch%' and c.currency_code::text like '%CLP%') then  (b.valor_venta::float/valor_uf.valor::float)::int else b.valor_venta end  "normalized_sales_price"
        ,b.m_construidos 
        ,b.m_terreno 
        ,b.dormitorios 
        ,b.banos 
        ,b.estacionamientos
        ,b.servicios 
        ,b.amoblado
        ,b.orientacion
        ,b.piscina
        ,b.gym
        ,b.mascotas
        ,b.calefaccion
        ,b.latitud 
        ,b.longitud 
        ,case when a.country = 'Chile' and c.status in ('published','republished') then concat('https://houm.com/cl/propiedades/venta/',concat(a.type,concat('/',concat(a.region,concat('/',concat(a.comuna,concat('/',a.id)))))))
              when a.country = 'Colombia' and c.status in ('published','republished') then concat('https://houm.com/co/propiedades/venta/',concat(a.type,concat('/',concat(a.region,concat('/',concat(a.comuna,concat('/',a.id)))))))
              when a.country = 'Mexico' and c.status in ('published','republished') then concat('https://houm.com/mx/propiedades/venta/',concat(a.type,concat('/',concat(a.region,concat('/',concat(a.comuna,concat('/',a.id)))))))
              else concat('https://houm.com/',concat(f.country_code,concat('/propiedades/',a.uid::text)))
              end as houm_link_marketplace
        --,d.geo_id
        ,e.name as macrozone
        ,e.city as  city_macrozone
        ,e.country as country_macrozone
        ,e.city_marketplace_id
        ,e.city_marketplace
FROM valor_uf, {{ ref('proc_properties') }} a
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_propertydetails') }} b on a.id = b.property_id 
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_property_salesdetails') }} c on a.id = c.property_id
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_properties_location') }}  f on a.neighborhood_id  = f.id 
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }}  d on d.property_id  = a.id 
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_macrozone') }} e on d.geo_id = e.geo_id 
where (b.status in ('published','republished')
or c.status in ('published','republished') ) AND a.is_deleted = False 
)
select * from tabla_final

model.houm.property__published_propertie.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

with valor_uf as (
    select valor from economic_indicator_uf 
    order by fecha desc
    limit 1
    )
, tabla_final as (
SELECT 
        a.property_id 
        ,valor_uf.valor as valor_uf
        ,a.valor
        ,a.valor_venta
        ,g.sale_suggested_price
        ,g.rental_suggested_price
        ,a.rentals_currency_code 
        ,a.sales_currency_code 
        ,g.rental_suggested_currency as rental_suggested_currency_code
        ,g.sale_suggested_currency as sale_suggested_currency_code
        ,g.sale_original_price
        ,g.rental_original_price
        ,case when a.valor_venta is null or a.valor_venta = 0 then null
          when g.sale_suggested_price is null or g.sale_suggested_price = 0 then null
          else (
                case    when a.sales_currency_code::text like '%CLP%' and g.sale_suggested_currency like '%CLF%'
                        then Round( (a.valor_venta/valor_uf.valor )::float / g.sale_suggested_price,3)
                        when a.sales_currency_code::text like '%CLF%' and g.sale_suggested_currency like '%CLP%'
                        then Round( (a.valor_venta*valor_uf.valor )::float / g.sale_suggested_price,3)
                        else Round( (a.valor_venta)::float / g.sale_suggested_price , 3)
                        end
                ) end rev_ratio_sales
        ,case when a.valor is null or a.valor = 0 then null
          when g.rental_suggested_price is null or g.rental_suggested_price = 0 then null
          else (
                case    when a.rentals_currency_code::text like '%CLP%' and g.rental_suggested_currency like '%CLF%'
                        then Round( (a.valor/valor_uf.valor )::float / g.rental_suggested_price,3)
                        when a.rentals_currency_code::text like '%CLF%' and g.rental_suggested_currency like '%CLP%'
                        then Round( (a.valor*valor_uf.valor )::float / g.rental_suggested_price,3)
                        else Round( (a.valor)::float / g.rental_suggested_price , 3)
                        end
                ) end rev_ratio_rentals 
FROM valor_uf, {{ ref('property__published_properties') }} a
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_properties_rev_suggested_prices') }} g on g.property_id = a.property_id
)
select * from tabla_final

model.houm.property__rev_kpi_ratio.raw_sql:
WITH sales AS (
        SELECT id,
            'sales' AS service_type, 
            'published' AS status,
            price/recommended_price AS recommended_price_ratio,
            price/min_recommended_price AS min_recommended_price_ratio,
            price/max_recommended_price AS max_recommended_price_ratio,
            country,
            city_marketplace
        FROM {{ ref('proc_rev_sales_published_properties') }}
        UNION ALL
        SELECT id,
            'sales' AS service_type,
            'taken' AS status,
            price/recommended_price AS recommended_price_ratio,
            price/min_recommended_price AS min_recommended_price_ratio,
            price/max_recommended_price AS max_recommended_price_ratio,
            country,
            city_marketplace
        FROM {{ ref('proc_rev_sales_sold_properties') }}
    ),
    rental AS (
        SELECT id,
            'rental' AS service_type,
            'published' AS status,
            price/recommended_price AS recommended_price_ratio,
            price/min_recommended_price AS min_recommended_price_ratio,
            price/max_recommended_price AS max_recommended_price_ratio,
            country,
            city_marketplace
        FROM {{ ref('proc_rev_rental_published_properties') }}
        UNION ALL
        SELECT id,
            'rental' AS service_type,
            'taken' AS status,
            price/recommended_price AS recommended_price_ratio,
            price/min_recommended_price AS min_recommended_price_ratio,
            price/max_recommended_price AS max_recommended_price_ratio,
            country,
            city_marketplace
        FROM {{ ref('proc_rev_rental_rented_properties') }}
    ),

ratio_by_id AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM sales
    UNION ALL 
    SELECT *
    FROM rental
    ),
ratio_treshold AS (
    SELECT PERCENTILE_CONT(0.955) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY recommended_price_ratio) As upper_val,
           PERCENTILE_CONT(0.045) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY recommended_price_ratio) As lower_val
    FROM ratio_by_id
)

SELECT *
FROM ratio_by_id, ratio_treshold
WHERE recommended_price_ratio IS NOT NULL
AND min_recommended_price_ratio IS NOT NULL
AND max_recommended_price_ratio IS NOT NULL
AND country IS NOT NULL
AND city_marketplace IS NOT NULL

model.houm.property__rev_kpi_ratio.compiled_sql:
WITH sales AS (
        SELECT id,
            'sales' AS service_type, 
            'published' AS status,
            price/recommended_price AS recommended_price_ratio,
            price/min_recommended_price AS min_recommended_price_ratio,
            price/max_recommended_price AS max_recommended_price_ratio,
            country,
            city_marketplace
        FROM "houmdw_prod"."dbt_processing"."proc_rev_sales_published_properties"
        UNION ALL
        SELECT id,
            'sales' AS service_type,
            'taken' AS status,
            price/recommended_price AS recommended_price_ratio,
            price/min_recommended_price AS min_recommended_price_ratio,
            price/max_recommended_price AS max_recommended_price_ratio,
            country,
            city_marketplace
        FROM "houmdw_prod"."dbt_processing"."proc_rev_sales_sold_properties"
    ),
    rental AS (
        SELECT id,
            'rental' AS service_type,
            'published' AS status,
            price/recommended_price AS recommended_price_ratio,
            price/min_recommended_price AS min_recommended_price_ratio,
            price/max_recommended_price AS max_recommended_price_ratio,
            country,
            city_marketplace
        FROM "houmdw_prod"."dbt_processing"."proc_rev_rental_published_properties"
        UNION ALL
        SELECT id,
            'rental' AS service_type,
            'taken' AS status,
            price/recommended_price AS recommended_price_ratio,
            price/min_recommended_price AS min_recommended_price_ratio,
            price/max_recommended_price AS max_recommended_price_ratio,
            country,
            city_marketplace
        FROM "houmdw_prod"."dbt_processing"."proc_rev_rental_rented_properties"
    ),

ratio_by_id AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM sales
    UNION ALL 
    SELECT *
    FROM rental
    ),
ratio_treshold AS (
    SELECT PERCENTILE_CONT(0.955) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY recommended_price_ratio) As upper_val,
           PERCENTILE_CONT(0.045) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY recommended_price_ratio) As lower_val
    FROM ratio_by_id
)

SELECT *
FROM ratio_by_id, ratio_treshold
WHERE recommended_price_ratio IS NOT NULL
AND min_recommended_price_ratio IS NOT NULL
AND max_recommended_price_ratio IS NOT NULL
AND country IS NOT NULL
AND city_marketplace IS NOT NULL
AND recommended_price_ratio < ratio_treshold.upper_val
AND recommended_price_ratio > ratio_treshold.lower_val

model.houm.property__rev_kpi_recommendat.raw_sql:
WITH median_ratio AS (SELECT
        service_type,
        status,
        country,
        city_marketplace,
        PERCENTILE_CONT(0.5) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY recommended_price_ratio) as median_price_ratio
    FROM {{ ref('property__rev_kpi_ratio') }}
    GROUP BY service_type, status, country, city_marketplace
    ),
    min_median_ratio AS (SELECT
        service_type,
        status,
        country,
        city_marketplace,
        PERCENTILE_CONT(0.5) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY min_recommended_price_ratio) as min_median_price_ratio
    FROM {{ ref('property__rev_kpi_ratio') }}
    GROUP BY service_type, status, country, city_marketplace
    ),
    max_median_ratio AS (SELECT
        service_type,
        status,
        country,
        city_marketplace,
        PERCENTILE_CONT(0.5) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY max_recommended_price_ratio) as max_median_price_ratio
    FROM {{ ref('property__rev_kpi_ratio') }}
    GROUP BY service_type, status, country, city_marketplace
    ), 
    average_ratio AS (
        SELECT
        service_type,
        status,
        country,
        city_marketplace,
        COUNT(*) as properties_counted,
        AVG(recommended_price_ratio) as average_price_ratio,
        AVG(min_recommended_price_ratio) as average_min_price_ratio,
        AVG(max_recommended_price_ratio) as average_max_price_ratio
    FROM {{ ref('property__rev_kpi_ratio') }} average_ratio
    GROUP BY service_type, status, country, city_marketplace
    ),
    stdev_ratio AS (
        SELECT
        service_type,
        status,
        country,
        city_marketplace,
        STDDEV(recommended_price_ratio) as stdev_price_ratio,
        STDDEV(min_recommended_price_ratio) as stdev_min_price_ratio,
        STDDEV(max_recommended_price_ratio) as stdev_max_price_ratio
    FROM {{ ref('property__rev_kpi_ratio') }}
    GROUP BY service_type, status, country, city_marketplace
    ),
    rev_kpi AS (
    SELECT average_ratio.service_type,
    average_ratio.country,
    average_ratio.city_marketplace,
    average_ratio.status,
    average_ratio.properties_counted,
    average_price_ratio,
    stdev_ratio.stdev_price_ratio,
    average_min_price_ratio,
    stdev_ratio.stdev_min_price_ratio,
    average_max_price_ratio,
    stdev_ratio.stdev_max_price_ratio,
    median_price_ratio,
    min_median_price_ratio,
    max_median_price_ratio
    FROM (average_ratio
        LEFT JOIN median_ratio
        ON (average_ratio.service_type = median_ratio.service_type
        AND average_ratio.status = median_ratio.status
        AND average_ratio.country = median_ratio.country
        AND average_ratio.city_marketplace = median_ratio.city_marketplace
        )
        LEFT JOIN min_median_ratio
        ON (average_ratio.service_type = min_median_ratio.service_type
        AND average_ratio.status = min_median_ratio.status
        AND average_ratio.country = min_median_ratio.country
        AND average_ratio.city_marketplace = min_median_ratio.city_marketplace
        )
        LEFT JOIN max_median_ratio
        ON (average_ratio.service_type = max_median_ratio.service_type
        AND average_ratio.status = max_median_ratio.status
        AND average_ratio.country = max_median_ratio.country
        AND average_ratio.city_marketplace = max_median_ratio.city_marketplace
        )
        LEFT JOIN stdev_ratio
        ON (average_ratio.service_type = stdev_ratio.service_type
        AND average_ratio.status = stdev_ratio.status
        AND average_ratio.country = stdev_ratio.country
        AND average_ratio.city_marketplace = stdev_ratio.city_marketplace
        )
        )
    )

    SELECT *
    FROM rev_kpi
    ORDER BY service_type,
             country,
             city_marketplace,
             status

model.houm.dim_dates.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='view') }}


 SELECT
    cast(seq + 1 AS INTEGER)                                      AS date_id,
-- DATE
    datum                                                         AS full_date,
    TO_CHAR(datum, 'DD/MM/YYYY') :: CHAR(10)                      AS au_format_date,
    TO_CHAR(datum, 'MM/DD/YYYY') :: CHAR(10)                      AS us_format_date,
-- YEAR
    cast(extract(YEAR FROM datum) AS SMALLINT)                    AS year_number,
    cast(extract(WEEK FROM datum) AS SMALLINT)                    AS year_week_number,
    cast(extract(DOY FROM datum) AS SMALLINT)                     AS year_day_number,
    cast(to_char(datum + INTERVAL '6' MONTH, 'yyyy') AS SMALLINT) AS au_fiscal_year_number,
    cast(to_char(datum + INTERVAL '3' MONTH, 'yyyy') AS SMALLINT) AS us_fiscal_year_number,
-- QUARTER
    cast(to_char(datum, 'Q') AS SMALLINT)                         AS qtr_number,
    cast(to_char(datum + INTERVAL '6' MONTH, 'Q') AS SMALLINT)    AS au_fiscal_qtr_number,
    cast(to_char(datum + INTERVAL '3' MONTH, 'Q') AS SMALLINT)    AS us_fiscal_qtr_number,
-- MONTH
    cast(extract(MONTH FROM datum) AS SMALLINT)                   AS month_number,
    to_char(datum, 'Month')                                       AS month_name,
    cast(extract(DAY FROM datum) AS SMALLINT)                     AS month_day_number,
-- WEEK
    cast(to_char(datum, 'D') AS SMALLINT)                         AS week_day_number,
-- DAY
    to_char(datum, 'Day')                                         AS day_name,
    CASE WHEN to_char(datum, 'D') IN ('1', '7')
      THEN 0
    ELSE 1 END                                                    AS day_is_weekday,
    CASE WHEN
      extract(DAY FROM (datum + (1 - extract(DAY FROM datum)) :: INTEGER +
                        INTERVAL '1' MONTH) :: DATE -
                       INTERVAL '1' DAY) = extract(DAY FROM datum)
      THEN 1
    ELSE 0 END                                                    AS day_is_last_of_month
  FROM
    (
      SELECT
        '2018-01-01' :: DATE + generate_series AS datum,
        generate_series                        AS seq
      FROM generate_series(0, 7 * 365, 1)
    ) DQ
  ORDER BY 1 desc

        ELSE Null END AS geo_id 
FROM pipedrive_cities
)

SELECT *
FROM dim_pipedrive_cities

            THEN 1

    END AS PastLastWeek ,
    CASE WHEN 
            DATE_TRUNC('month',begin_date_agg) = DATE_TRUNC('month','2022-09-14 13:53:27.792943-03:00'::DATE)

            THEN 1
        ELSE 0

    CASE 
        WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month', begin_date_agg ) = DATEADD(MONTH,-3, DATE_TRUNC('month','2022-09-14 13:53:27.792943-03:00'::DATE) )

model.houm.fact_daily_virtual_uf_cl.raw_sql:
with table6 as (
select row_number() over (order by thedate asc) as n_day
 	,thefirstofmonth 
 	,thedate
 	,b.monthly_inflation
 	,b.daily_inflation
 	,lead(daily_inflation,1) over (order by thedate asc) as next_daily_inflation
from dim_dates a
left join {{ ref('proc_monthly_daily_inflation_cl') }} b on a.thefirstofmonth  = b.date_formatted 
order by thedate asc
)
, table7 as (
select thedate
		,n_day
		,monthly_inflation
		,daily_inflation
		--,(SUM(1 * (1+daily_inflation) ) OVER(ORDER BY thedate ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW)-(n_day-1)) as try_1
from table6
where monthly_inflation is not null
order by n_day
)

select 
	n_day
	,thedate
	,monthly_inflation
	,daily_inflation
	,exp(sum(ln(1+daily_inflation)) over (ORDER BY thedate ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW)) as  daily_virtual_uf
from table7

model.houm.cum_rentals_units.raw_sql:
SELECT
    'rentals_transactions' as metric,
    'acc_units' as col,
    country,
    date_month,
    SUM(total) over (
        PARTITION BY country
        ORDER BY
            date_month rows unbounded preceding
    ) AS cum_total
FROM
    {{ ref('rentals_units') }}
WHERE date_month >= concat(extract(year from current_date),'-01-01')
ORDER BY
    country,
    date_month

model.houm.goals_current.raw_sql:
WITH GoalsCurrent AS (
SELECT *
FROM {{ ref('rentals_units') }}
UNION ALL
SELECT *
FROM {{ ref('sales_units') }}
UNION ALL
SELECT *
FROM {{ref('sales_local_revenue')}}
UNION ALL
SELECT *
FROM {{ref('eop_subs')}}
UNION ALL 
SELECT *
FROM {{ref('cum_sales_units')}}
UNION ALL 
SELECT *
FROM {{ref('cum_rentals_units')}}
UNION ALL 
SELECT *
FROM {{ref('cum_sales_local_revenue')}})

SELECT 
/* NO PIVOT IN REDSHIFT */
SUM(CASE WHEN col = 'units' THEN total END) as units,
SUM(CASE WHEN col = 'acc_units' THEN total END) as acc_units,
SUM(CASE WHEN col = 'local_revenue' THEN total END) AS local_revenue,
SUM(CASE WHEN col = 'acc_local_revenue' THEN total END) AS acc_local_revenue,
metric,country,date_month
FROM GoalsCurrent
GROUP BY country,metric,date_month

model.houm.properties_published.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

SELECT 
        a.id as property_id
        ,b.status as rental_status
        ,c.status as sales_status
        ,a.*
FROM {{ ref('proc_properties') }} a
left join {{ ref('proc_propertydetails') }} b on a.id = b.property_id 
left join {{ ref('proc_property_salesdetails') }} c on a.id = c.property_id
where b.status in ('published','republished') or c.status in ('published','republished')

model.houm.rental_landlord_metric_leads.name: rental_landlord_metric_leads
model.houm.rental_landlord_metric_leads.compiled_sql:
WITH metric AS (
SELECT 
	* 
FROM "houmdw_prod"."dbt_facts"."rental_landlord_metric_details_leads"
)

SELECT 
        orden ,  
        metric ,	
        geo_id ,
        COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN yesterday = 1 THEN person_email END ) yesterday,  
        COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN daybeforeyesterday = 1 THEN person_email END ) daybeforeyesterday,  
        COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LastWeek = 1 THEN person_email END ) LastWeek,  
        COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PastLastWeek = 1 THEN person_email END ) PastLastWeek,  
        COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN ThisMonthtoday = 1 THEN person_email END ) ThisMonthtoday,  
        COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LastMonthtoday = 1 THEN person_email END ) LastMonthtoday,  
        COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LastMonth = 1 THEN person_email END ) LastMonth,  
        COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LasttwoMonth = 1 THEN person_email END ) LasttwoMonth,  
        COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LastthreeMonth = 1 THEN person_email END ) LastthreeMonth 
    from metric 
    group by 1,2,3

model.houm.proc_closure_contract_histori.raw_sql:
WITH contratcs AS (
SELECT
    contracts.id 
FROM {{ ref('stg_contracts') }} AS contracts 
)

, contracts_historical_renamestatus AS (
SELECT
    contratcs.id ,
    historical_contracts.audit_start_dt ,
    historical_contracts.audit_end_dt ,
    COALESCE(NULLIF(historical_contracts.status,'') , 'NotStatus' ) AS status ,
    COALESCE(NULLIF(historical_contracts.online_process_status,'') , 'NotStatus') AS online_process_status ,
    COALESCE(NULLIF(historical_contracts.status,'') , 'NotStatus' ) || '-' || COALESCE(NULLIF(historical_contracts.online_process_status,'') , 'NotStatus') AS status_key
FROM contratcs
INNER JOIN historical.historical_contracts AS historical_contracts
    ON contratcs.id = historical_contracts.id
WHERE TRUE

)
, contract_updates_count AS (
SELECT
    id ,
    audit_start_dt ,
    audit_end_dt ,
    status ,
    online_process_status ,
    status_key ,
    CASE
        WHEN ( (lag(status_key) OVER (PARTITION BY id ORDER BY audit_start_dt ASC ) ) = status_key ) THEN 0
        ELSE 1
    END AS status_has_changed
FROM contracts_historical_renamestatus
WHERE true
ORDER BY id DESC, audit_start_dt
)

, contract_status_index AS (
SELECT
    id ,
    audit_start_dt ,
    COALESCE(audit_end_dt, '{{ var("processed_time") }}') AS audit_end_dt , 
    status ,
    online_process_status ,
    status_key ,
    SUM(status_has_changed) OVER (PARTITION BY id ORDER BY audit_start_dt ASC ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW ) AS status_index
FROM contract_updates_count
ORDER BY id DESC , audit_start_dt ASC
)

, contract_statuses_periods AS (
SELECT
    id ,
    status_index ,
    status_key ,
    status,
    online_process_status ,
    MIN(audit_start_dt) AS date_start ,
    NULLIF( MAX(audit_end_dt) ,  '{{ var("processed_time") }}' ) AS date_end  
FROM contract_status_index
GROUP BY 1 ,2,3,4, 5
)

, contracts_translation AS (
 SELECT
    contract_statuses_periods.id ,
    CASE
        WHEN contract_statuses_periods.status IN ('Rechazado','Rechazado por Propietario','Desistido') THEN 'Perdido'
        WHEN contract_statuses_periods.status = 'Pagado' THEN 'Pagado'
        WHEN contract_statuses_periods.status IN ('Generar boton de pago','Boton de pago enviado') THEN 'Boton de pago'
        WHEN contract_statuses_periods.status = 'Listo para redaccion' THEN 'Firmas'
        WHEN contract_statuses_periods.status IN ('Aprobacion propietario', 'Perfil enviado' , 'Aprobado por propietario') THEN 'Aprobación Propietario'
        ELSE 'Otro'
    END macro_status ,
    contract_statuses_periods.status_index ,
    contract_statuses_periods.status ,
    contract_statuses_periods.online_process_status ,
    CASE contract_statuses_periods.online_process_status
        WHEN 'Pending' THEN 'Pendiente'
        WHEN 'Links sent lessor' THEN 'Contrato enviado propietario'
        WHEN 'Links sent others' THEN 'Contrato enviado postulante'
        WHEN 'Signatures completed' THEN 'Contrato firmado ambas partes'
        WHEN 'Finalized' then 'Finalizado'
        ELSE contract_statuses_periods.online_process_status
    END AS online_process_status_translation ,
    contract_statuses_periods.date_start ,
    contract_statuses_periods.date_end ,
    '{{ var("processed_time") }}' AS processed_time
FROM contract_statuses_periods
ORDER BY id DESC, Status_index DESC
)

SELECT
    *
FROM contracts_translation
ORDER BY id , status_index

		nps.name,

		CASE
			WHEN nps.property_id ='-' THEN null
			ELSE nps.property_id::integer
		END AS property_id, 
        CASE
            WHEN nps.source = 1 THEN '1.Publicidad'
            WHEN nps.source = 2 THEN '2.Google'
            WHEN nps.source = 3 THEN '3.Me lo recomendaron'
            WHEN nps.source = 4 THEN '4.Redes sociales'
            WHEN nps.source = 5 THEN '5.De un portal de propiedades'
            WHEN nps.source = 6 THEN '6.Otro'
            ELSE NULL
        END AS source, 
		CASE
			WHEN left(contract_signature,1) BETWEEN 0 AND 9 THEN nps.contract_signature::integer
			ELSE NULL
		END AS contract_signature,
		CASE
			WHEN left(nps.recommendation,1) BETWEEN 0 AND 9 THEN nps.recommendation::integer
			ELSE NULL
		END AS recommendation,
		nps.comments
   FROM {{ref('stg_whatsapp_nps_rentas_propietary_pc')}} nps
   ),
nps_survicate AS (

		nps*100 AS nps,
		'' AS name,
		'' AS phone,
		'propietary_poscontract' AS role,
		country,
		first_response_date::timestamp,

            WHEN sc1_customer_source = 'Publicidad' THEN '1.Publicidad'
            WHEN sc1_customer_source = 'Googleando' THEN '2.Google'

            WHEN sc1_customer_source = 'De un portal de propiedades' THEN '5.De un portal de propiedades'
            WHEN sc1_customer_source = 'Otro' THEN '6.Otro'
            ELSE NULL
        END AS source,
        CASE m1_contract_signing_easiness

        	WHEN 'De acuerdo' THEN 8
        	WHEN 'Neutro' THEN 6
        	WHEN 'Desacuerdo' THEN 4
        	WHEN 'Muy en desacuerdo' THEN 2

        END AS contract_signature,
        nps_service_recommendation,
        CASE

            ELSE "left"(nps."timestamp"::text, 10)::date
        END AS date,
        CASE
            WHEN nps."timestamp" IS NULL OR nps."timestamp"::text = ''::character varying::text THEN '00:00:00'::time without time zone
            ELSE "left"("right"(nps."timestamp"::text, 9), 8)::time without time zone
        END AS "time",
        CASE
            WHEN nps.recommendation IN (9,10) THEN 100::numeric(18, 0)
               WHEN nps.recommendation IN (7,8) THEN 0.00
               WHEN nps.recommendation IN (0,6) THEN - 100::numeric(18, 0)
               ELSE NULL
        END AS nps,

            WHEN nps.source = 5 THEN '5.De un portal de propiedades'
            WHEN nps.source = 6 THEN '6.Otro'
            ELSE NULL
        END AS source,
           nps.process_quickness,
           nps.process_clarity,
           nps.recommendation,

           case when role like '%rent%' then 'Rentals'

with nps_whatsapp_raw as (
    select 
        appraiser, 
        schedule_id,

			when '-' then null
			else cast(property_id as integer) 
		end as property_id,
        to_date(np."date",'DD/MM/YYYY') as date, 
        np."time"::time, 
        address,
		case trim(houmer_service)
			when '-' then null
			else cast(houmer_service as integer) end as houmer_service,
		case trim(houmer_knowledge)
			when '-' then null
			else cast(houmer_knowledge as integer) end as houmer_knowledge,
		case trim(schedule_easyness) 
			when '-' then null
			else cast(schedule_easyness as integer) end as schedule_easyness,
		case trim(visit_success) 
			when '-' then null
			else cast(visit_success as integer) end as visit_success,
		case trim(recommendation) 
			when '-' then null
			else cast(recommendation as integer) end as recommendation,
		country, 
		comments
    from {{ref('stg_whatsapp_nps_photo')}} np
),
nps_whatsapp as (
    select 
        nps_whatsapp_raw.*,
        hss.business,
		case when recommendation in (9,10) then 100
			when recommendation in (7,8) then 0.00
			when recommendation in (1,2,3,4,5,6) then -100
			else null end as NPS

),

    select 
        null as appraiser, 
        null as schedule_id, 
        null as property_id,
        left(first_response_date,10)::date as date, 
        right(first_response_date,8)::time as time,
        null as address,
        m1_houmer_during_visit*2 as houmer_service,
        m1_houmer_before_visit*2 as houmer_knowledge,
        m1_website_simplicity*2 as schedule_easyness,
        case property_photos_experience when 'Extremely happy' then 10
            when 'Happy' then 8
            when 'Neutral' then 6
            when 'Unsatisfied' then 4
            when 'Extremely unsatisfied' then 2
            else null
        end as visit_success,
        null as recommendation,
        country,
        case when text1_bad_answer = '' then case when text1_neutral_answer = '' then '' else text1_neutral_answer end else 'Bad:'||text1_bad_answer || ' Neutral: '|| text1_neutral_answer end as comments,
        '' as business,
        nps*100 as nps
    from {{ref('stg_survicate_nps_photo_done')}} 
    where date < '2021-10-21'
)
SELECT 
    * 
FROM 
    nps_whatsapp
UNION ALL
SELECT
    * 
FROM 
    nps_survicate
ORDER BY "date" DESC, "time" DESC

model.houm.proc_cx_nps_visit_cancelled.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH nps_visits_cancelled AS (
	SELECT 
        address,
		country,
		comments,
		appraiser,
		visit_type,
		schedule_id,
		property_id,
		(split_part(begin_date,'-',3)||'-'||split_part(begin_date,'-',2)||'-'||split_part(begin_date,'-',1))::date AS begin_date,
		answered_at,
		recommendation 
	FROM {{ref('stg_whatsapp_nps_visits_cancelled')}} acv 
)
,scheduler_schedules AS (
	SELECT 
        schedule_id AS id, 
        begin_date
	FROM {{ref('proc_tmp_demand_schedules_cleaned')}}
	WHERE 
		STATUS = 'Cancelled'	
		AND begin_date BETWEEN '2022-01-08' AND '{{ var("processed_time") }}'::date
)
,clean_nps AS (
	SELECT 
        INITCAP(LOWER(nvc.country)) AS country,
		nvc.visit_type,
		nvc.schedule_id,
		nvc.property_id,
		coalesce(nvc.begin_date,scheduler_schedules.begin_date) as begin_date,
		coalesce(answered_at,scheduler_schedules.begin_date,nvc.begin_date) AS formated_answer_timestamp,
		nvc.address,
		nvc.appraiser,
		nvc.recommendation::integer,
		nvc.comments
	FROM nps_visits_cancelled nvc 
	LEFT JOIN scheduler_schedules ON scheduler_schedules.id = nvc.schedule_id 
)
SELECT 
    clean_nps.*, 
	formated_answer_timestamp::date AS formated_answer_date,
	to_char(formated_answer_timestamp,'HH24:MI:SS') AS formated_answer_time 
FROM clean_nps

model.houm.proc_cx_nps_visit_done.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH scheduler_schedules AS (
	SELECT 
		schedule_id as id,
		appraiser_id 
	FROM {{ref('proc_tmp_demand_schedules_cleaned')}} hss 
),
scheduler_appraisers AS (
	SELECT 
		id,
		name 
	FROM {{ref('stg_scheduler_appraisers')}} 
), 
raw_nps_whatsapp as (
	SELECT 
		appraiser, 
		schedule_id::integer, 
		property_id::integer, 
		to_date("date",'DD/MM/YYYY') as "date",
		"time"::time without time zone, 
		address,
		CASE houmer_service
			WHEN '-' THEN null
			ELSE houmer_service::integer
		END as houmer_service,
		CASE houmer_knowledge
			WHEN '-' THEN null
			ELSE houmer_knowledge::integer
		END as houmer_knowledge,
		CASE schedule_easyness 
			WHEN '-' then null
			ELSE schedule_easyness::integer
		END as schedule_easyness,
		CASE visit_success 
			WHEN '-' THEN null
			else cast(visit_success as integer) end as visit_success,
		CASE recommendation 
			WHEN '-' THEN null
			ELSE recommendation::integer
		END as recommendation,
		country,
		business,
		comments
	FROM {{ref('stg_whatsapp_nps_visits_done')}}
),
nps_whatsapp AS (
SELECT 
    scheduler_appraisers.name AS appraiser, 
    q.schedule_id,
	q.property_id,
	q.date,
    q.time,
    q.address,
    q.recommendation,
    q.country,
    q.business,
    q.comments, 
    CASE
        WHEN q.recommendation IN (9,10) THEN 100
		WHEN q.recommendation IN (7,8) THEN 0.00
		WHEN q.recommendation IN (1,2,3,4,5,6) THEN -100
		ELSE null 
	END AS NPS,
	houmer_service,
	houmer_knowledge,
	schedule_easyness AS schedule_easiness,
	visit_success
FROM raw_nps_whatsapp AS q
LEFT JOIN scheduler_schedules ON scheduler_schedules.id = q.schedule_id
LEFT JOIN scheduler_appraisers ON scheduler_appraisers.id = scheduler_schedules.appraiser_id
ORDER BY "date" ASC, "time" ASC
),
nps_survicate AS (
	SELECT 		
		'' as appraiser ,
		null::integer as schedule_id,
		null::integer as property_id,
		"left"(nps.first_response_date::text, 10)::date AS date, 
		"right"(nps.first_response_date::text, 8)::time without time zone AS "time", 
		'' as address,
		nps.nps_service_recommendation::integer AS nps_service_recommendation, 
		nps.country, 
		'' as business, 
        CASE
        	WHEN nps.text1_bad_answer = '' THEN 
                CASE
                    WHEN nps.text1_neutral_answer = '' THEN 
                    	CASE
                        	WHEN nps.text1_good_answer = '' THEN ''
                        	ELSE 'Good: ' || nps.text1_good_answer
                    	END
                    ELSE 'Neutral: ' || nps.text1_neutral_answer
                END
            ELSE (((('Bad: ' || nps.text1_bad_answer) || ' Neutral: ') || nps.text1_neutral_answer) || ' Good: ') || nps.text1_good_answer
        END AS comments,
        nps.nps * 100 AS nps, 
        null AS houmer_service, 
        CASE
            WHEN nps.m1_houmer_delivers_info::text = 'Muy de acuerdo'::text THEN 10
            WHEN nps.m1_houmer_delivers_info::text = 'De acuerdo'::text THEN 8
            WHEN nps.m1_houmer_delivers_info::text = 'Neutro'::text THEN 6
            WHEN nps.m1_houmer_delivers_info::text = 'Desacuerdo'::text THEN 4
            WHEN nps.m1_houmer_delivers_info::text = 'Muy en desacuerdo'::text THEN 2
            ELSE null
        END AS houmer_knowledge, 
        CASE
        	WHEN nps.m1_schedule_easiness::text = 'Muy de acuerdo' THEN 10
            WHEN nps.m1_schedule_easiness::text = 'De acuerdo' THEN 8
            WHEN nps.m1_schedule_easiness::text = 'Neutro' THEN 6
            WHEN nps.m1_schedule_easiness::text = 'Desacuerdo' THEN 4
            WHEN nps.m1_schedule_easiness::text = 'Muy en desacuerdo' THEN 2
        	ELSE null
        END AS schedule_easiness,
        null as visit_success
    FROM {{ref('stg_survicate_nps_visit_done')}} nps
    WHERE nps.first_response_date::date <= '2021-10-24'::date
	)
SELECT * 
FROM nps_whatsapp
UNION ALL
SELECT * 
FROM nps_survicate

model.houm.proc_app_cancelations.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}
SELECT 
    scheduler_schedules.id schedule_id ,
    scheduler_cancelreasons.id cancelation_id ,
    scheduler_cancelreasontypes.cancel_type ,
    scheduler_cancelreasontypes.cancel_reason ,
    scheduler_cancelreasontypes.roles ,
    scheduler_cancelreasontypes.text cancel_reason_text ,
    scheduler_cancelreasons.comment ,
    scheduler_appraiserevent.created_at cancelled_at ,
    scheduler_appraiserevent.latitude latitude_appraiser ,
    scheduler_appraiserevent.longitude longitude_appraiser ,
    scheduler_appraisers.id appraiser_id ,
    scheduler_appraisers.name name_appraiser ,
    scheduler_appraisers.email email_appraiser ,
    CASE WHEN scheduler_schedules.begin_date >= scheduler_appraiserevent.created_at THEN 'Pre-Visit'::text
         WHEN scheduler_schedules.begin_date < scheduler_appraiserevent.created_at THEN 'Post-Visit'::text
         ELSE NULL END AS cancel_timing
FROM {{ ref('stg_scheduler_cancelreasons') }} scheduler_cancelreasons        
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_scheduler_schedules') }} scheduler_schedules
    ON scheduler_schedules.selected_cancel_reason_id = scheduler_cancelreasons.id 
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_scheduler_cancelreasontypes') }} scheduler_cancelreasontypes
    ON scheduler_cancelreasontypes.id = scheduler_cancelreasons.type_id 
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_scheduler_appraiserevent') }} scheduler_appraiserevent 
    ON scheduler_appraiserevent.schedule_id = scheduler_schedules.id 
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_scheduler_appraisers') }} scheduler_appraisers
    ON scheduler_appraisers.id = scheduler_schedules.appraiser_id
WHERE scheduler_appraiserevent.action = 'Cancelled'

    scheduler_appraisers.email email_appraiser ,
    CASE WHEN scheduler_schedules.begin_date >= scheduler_appraiserevent.created_at THEN 'Pre-Visit'::text

         ELSE NULL END AS cancel_timing

LEFT JOIN "houmdw_prod"."dbt_staging"."stg_scheduler_cancelreasontypes" scheduler_cancelreasontypes
    ON scheduler_cancelreasontypes.id = scheduler_cancelreasons.type_id 
LEFT JOIN "houmdw_prod"."dbt_staging"."stg_scheduler_appraiserevent" scheduler_appraiserevent 
    ON scheduler_appraiserevent.schedule_id = scheduler_schedules.id 
LEFT JOIN "houmdw_prod"."dbt_staging"."stg_scheduler_appraisers" scheduler_appraisers
    ON scheduler_appraisers.id = scheduler_schedules.appraiser_id
WHERE scheduler_appraiserevent.action = 'Cancelled'

model.houm.proc_core_scheduler_schedules.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}
WITH schedules AS (
SELECT 
    scheduler_schedules.id AS schedule_id ,
    scheduler_schedules.begin_date ,
    scheduler_schedules.end_date ,
    scheduler_schedules.updated_at ,
    scheduler_schedules.prop_id AS property_id ,
    proc_properties_mz.geo_id ,
    scheduler_schedules.status ,
    scheduler_scheduletypes.name AS visit_type ,
    scheduler_schedulehasapplicant.applicant_id
FROM {{ ref('stg_scheduler_schedules') }} AS scheduler_schedules
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_scheduler_scheduletypes') }} AS scheduler_scheduletypes
    ON scheduler_schedules.schedule_type_id = scheduler_scheduletypes.id 
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }} AS proc_properties_mz
    ON proc_properties_mz.property_id = scheduler_schedules.prop_id 
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_scheduler_schedulehasapplicant') }} AS scheduler_schedulehasapplicant
    ON scheduler_schedulehasapplicant.schedule_id = scheduler_schedules.id 
)
, rescheduled AS (
SELECT 
    id ,
    schedule_id ,
    created_at
FROM {{ ref('stg_scheduler_scheduleevent') }} AS scheduler_scheduleevent
WHERE action IN  ('Reschedule', 'Rescheduled')
)
, rescheduled_max AS (
SELECT
    a.*
FROM rescheduled AS a
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT
        schedule_id ,
        MAX(created_at) AS created_at
    FROM rescheduled
    GROUP BY schedule_id
) AS b
     ON a.created_at = b.created_at AND a.schedule_id = b.schedule_id
)
SELECT
    schedules.* ,
    rescheduled_max.created_at AS rescheduled_at ,
    CASE
        WHEN rescheduled_max.id IS NOT NULL THEN true
        ELSE false
    END AS is_reschedule
FROM schedules
LEFT JOIN rescheduled_max
    ON schedules.schedule_id = rescheduled_max.schedule_id

model.houm.proc_demand_leads.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH rental_properties AS (
SELECT 
	id AS property_id 
FROM {{ ref('proc_properties') }}
WHERE TRUE
	AND for_rental = TRUE
)

, demand_leads_clean AS (
SELECT * 
FROM {{ ref('stg_demand_lead') }} AS demand_leads
WHERE TRUE 
	AND ( ( email NOT LIKE '%test.test' AND email NOT LIKE '%test.com') OR email IS NULL )
)

, pa_leads AS (
SELECT 
	'PA -' || demand_portalapplicant.id AS activity_id ,
	lead_id ,
	COALESCE((timezone( prop_mz.timezone, demand_portalapplicant.created_at)::timestamp with time zone)::date,demand_portalapplicant.created_at::date) AS created_at ,
	COALESCE(origin, 'Portal No Identificado')  AS origin ,
	prop_mz.geo_id 
	--Falta agregar logica de cuando no tienen prop_id, por ejemplo incluir el pais en funcion al tipo de telefono.
FROM {{ ref('stg_demand_portalapplicant') }} AS demand_portalapplicant
INNER JOIN demand_leads_clean 
	ON demand_leads_clean.id = demand_portalapplicant.lead_id  -- Con inner Eliminar leads Test
INNER JOIN rental_properties 
	ON rental_properties.property_id = demand_portalapplicant.property_id  -- Con el inner join tengo los Lead de rentals ya que esta tabla de properties es solo de Rentals.  
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }} AS prop_mz 
	ON prop_mz.property_id = rental_properties.property_id
WHERE TRUE 
	AND ( origin != 'Test' OR origin IS NULL) 
)

, houm_leads AS ( 
SELECT      
	'HOUM -' || demand_portalhoum.id AS activity_id ,
	lead_id ,
	COALESCE((timezone( prop_mz.timezone, demand_portalhoum.created_at)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE )::DATE,demand_portalhoum.created_at::DATE) AS created_at ,
	'Houm' AS origin , 
	prop_mz.geo_id 
FROM {{ ref('stg_demand_portalhoum') }} demand_portalhoum
INNER JOIN demand_leads_clean 
	ON demand_leads_clean.id = demand_portalhoum.lead_id
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }} AS prop_mz
	ON prop_mz.property_id = demand_portalhoum.property_id
WHERE TRUE 
	AND business_type = 'rentals' 
)

, demand_leads AS (
SELECT 
	* 
FROM pa_leads
UNION ALL 
SELECT 
	* 
FROM houm_leads
)

SELECT *
FROM demand_leads

model.houm.proc_demand_marketingapplican.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='view') }}

WITH city_lead AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT id                                    AS lead_id,
                    country,
                    city,
                    CASE
                        WHEN country LIKE 'cl' THEN 79::INT
                        WHEN country LIKE 'co' THEN 14::INT
                        WHEN country LIKE 'mx' THEN 19::INT
                        ELSE NULL END                     AS geo_id_country,
                    CASE
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Medell%n%' THEN 31::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Bogot%' THEN 14::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Región Metropolitana%' THEN 79::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Santiago%' THEN 79::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Valparaíso%' THEN 11::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Concepción%' THEN 8::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Bío Bío%' THEN 8::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Ciudad de México%' THEN 19::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%México%' THEN 19::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Monterrey%' THEN 54::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Nuevo Leó%' THEN 54::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%MTY%' THEN 54::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Tijuana%' THEN 67::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Guadalajara%' THEN 30::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Puebla%' THEN 19::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Querétaro%' THEN 19::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%GDL%' THEN 30::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%CDMX%' THEN 19::INT
                        ELSE NULL END                     AS geo_id_city,
                    COALESCE(geo_id_city, geo_id_country) AS geo_id_lead
    FROM {{ ref('stg_demand_lead') }}
)
, stg_demand_marketingapplicant AS (
SELECT  demand_marketingapplicant.id,
        demand_marketingapplicant.created_at,
        demand_marketingapplicant.updated_at,
        demand_marketingapplicant.lead_id,

model.houm.proc_demand_pipedrive_deals.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH proc_properties_mz AS (
SELECT *
FROM {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }}  
)

, pipedrive_city AS (
SELECT *
FROM {{ ref('dim_pipedrive_city') }} 
)

, deals AS (
SELECT 
    id ,
    add_time ,
    email ,
    phone ,
    person_id , 
    CASE
        WHEN bi_deals.country_formated LIKE '%_hile%' THEN 79::INT
        WHEN bi_deals.country_formated LIKE '%_olombia%' THEN 14::INT
        WHEN bi_deals.country_formated LIKE '%__xico%' THEN 19::INT
        ELSE Null END AS geo_id_country_funnel ,
    CASE bi_deals.funnel 
        WHEN '1. Supply' THEN 'Supply' 
        WHEN '2. Demand' THEN 'Demand' 
        END AS funnel ,
    CASE 
        WHEN bi_deals.business IN ('2. Sales', '5. Sales Subsidio','5.1 Sales B2B' )    THEN 'Sales'
        WHEN bi_deals.business IN ('1. Rentals','3. Rental Alianzas' )                  THEN 'Rental'
        WHEN bi_deals.business IN ('4.1 Rental/Sales Alianzas', '4. Rental/Sales' )     THEN 'Rental & Sales'
        ELSE NULL END business ,
    CASE WHEN bi_deals.source like '%Autoperfilamiento%' THEN TRUE 
        ELSE FALSE END is_selfprofiling , 
    --- before negotiation
    --------------------
    bi_deals.marketing_id AS campaign_id , 
    bi_deals.source , 
    cities_source.geo_id as geo_id_source , 
    -- Demand 
    CASE 
        WHEN bi_deals.label = 345 THEN 'New Properties'
        WHEN bi_deals.label = 345 THEN 'Usados'
        ELSE NULL END AS buyer_relation_source   ,
    --- after negotiation
    --------------------
    COALESCE(proc_properties_mz.geo_id, cities_negotiation.geo_id) AS geo_id_negotiation , 
    bi_deals.property_id ,
    bi_deals.lead_buyer_type AS buyer_relation_negotiation ,
    -- Supply data 
    bi_deals.fecha_calificacion::date   AS supply_qualification_date , 
    bi_deals.qualification              AS supply_qualification ,
    -- Demand Data 
    CASE 
        WHEN bi_deals.fecha_calificacion::DATE < '2022-06-06'::DATE AND calificacion_buyer in (3,4,5) THEN coalesce(bi_deals.buyer_lead_qualification_date::DATE,bi_deals.fecha_calificacion::DATE)  
        WHEN bi_deals.fecha_calificacion::DATE < '2022-06-06'::DATE THEN NULL 
        ELSE bi_deals.buyer_lead_qualification_date::DATE 
        END AS buyer_qualification_date , 
    bi_deals.calificacion_buyer AS buyer_qualification , 
    -------------------
    bi_deals.lost_reason ,
    bi_deals.lost_time 
FROM {{ ref('stg_bi_deals') }} AS bi_deals
LEFT JOIN pipedrive_city AS cities_source 
    ON cities_source.city = bi_deals.city_3
LEFT JOIN pipedrive_city AS cities_negotiation
    ON cities_negotiation.city = bi_deals.city_2
LEFT JOIN proc_properties_mz
    ON proc_properties_mz.property_id = bi_deals.property_id
)

Select *
FROM deals

model.houm.proc_demand_pipedrive_leads.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH properties AS (
SELECT 
    id , 
    supply_source ,
    supply_relation ,
    country 
FROM {{ ref('proc_properties') }}
)

, proc_properties_mz AS (
SELECT *
FROM {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }}  
)

, demand_pipedrive_leads AS (
SELECT     
    -- Person details 
    persons.id AS person_id ,
    persons.name AS person_name ,
    COALESCE(persons.email , deals.email) AS email ,
    COALESCE(persons.phone , deals.phone) AS phone ,
    --- Pipedrive Info
    deals.id AS deal_id ,
    deals.add_time::DATE AS add_time  , 
    deals.funnel ,
    deals.business ,
    deals.geo_id_country_funnel ,
    deals.is_selfprofiling , 
    --- before negotiation
    deals.campaign_id , 
    deals.source , 
    geo_id_source , 
    -- Demand
    deals.buyer_relation_source ,
    --- after negotiation
    ---------------------------
    deals.property_id ,
    COALESCE( prop_mz.geo_id,  geo_id_negotiation, geo_id_country_funnel) AS geo_id_negotiation ,
    -- Supply data 
    --------------------
    deals.supply_qualification_date , 
    deals.supply_qualification , 
    -- Demand data
    --------------------
    CASE 
        WHEN  funnel = 'Demand' AND business LIKE '%Sales%' 
            THEN COALESCE( 
                        CASE 
                            WHEN properties.supply_source like 'New Properties' THEN properties.supply_source
                            WHEN properties.supply_source is not null THEN 'Usados'
                            END 
                        ,   buyer_relation_negotiation)
        ELSE NULL END  buyer_relation_negotiation ,
    properties.supply_relation ,
    properties.supply_source , 
    deals.buyer_qualification_date ,
    deals.buyer_qualification , 
    deals.lost_reason ,
    deals.lost_time 
FROM {{ref('proc_demand_pipedrive_deals')}} AS deals
LEFT JOIN {{ref('stg_bi_persons')}} AS persons
    ON deals.person_id = persons.id
LEFT JOIN proc_properties_mz AS prop_mz
    ON prop_mz.property_id = deals.property_id
LEFT JOIN properties 
    ON prop_mz.property_id = properties.id
WHERE add_time > '2022-01-01'::date
)

SELECT * 
FROM demand_pipedrive_leads

model.houm.proc_demand_portalapplicant.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='view') }}


WITH rental_properties AS (
    SELECT id        AS property_id,
           'rentals' AS business_type_property
    FROM {{ ref('proc_properties') }}
    WHERE TRUE
      AND for_rental = TRUE
)
   , sales_properties AS (
    SELECT id      AS property_id,
           'sales' AS business_type_property
    FROM {{ ref('proc_properties') }}
    WHERE TRUE
      AND for_sale = TRUE
)
   , union_properties AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM rental_properties
    UNION
    SELECT *
    FROM sales_properties
)
    , stg_demand_portalapplicant AS (
    SELECT demand_portalapplicant.id,
           demand_portalapplicant.created_at,
           demand_portalapplicant.updated_at,
           demand_portalapplicant.phone,
           demand_portalapplicant.email,
           demand_portalapplicant.lead_id,
           demand_portalapplicant.name,
           demand_portalapplicant.last_name,
           demand_portalapplicant.origin,
           demand_portalapplicant.property_id,
           demand_portalapplicant.business_type AS business_type_lead,
           union_properties.business_type_property,
           COALESCE(business_type_lead, business_type_property) AS business_type,
           properties_mz.geo_id,
           dim_mz.country,
           dim_mz.region_houm
    FROM {{ ref('stg_demand_portalapplicant') }} AS demand_portalapplicant
        LEFT JOIN union_properties
            ON demand_portalapplicant.property_id = union_properties.property_id 
            AND demand_portalapplicant.business_type IS NULL
    --hacemos este UNION porque en el pasado no traiamos el business_type del lead, en este join duplicamos las filas para los leads que vieron props de ambos negocios y en la epoca que no sabiamos el negocio exacto
        LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }} AS properties_mz
            ON demand_portalapplicant.property_id = properties_mz.property_id
        LEFT JOIN {{ ref('dim_macrozones') }} AS dim_mz
            ON properties_mz.geo_id = dim_mz.geo_id
    WHERE TRUE
      AND demand_portalapplicant.origin != 'Houm' --limpiamos los leads con origen de portal como "Houm" porque ya estan considerados en demand_portalhoum, y en el pasado esta tabla los duplicaba
)
  
SELECT  id,
        created_at,
        updated_at,
        name,
        last_name,
        phone,
        email,
        lead_id,
        origin,
        property_id,
        business_type,
        geo_id,
        country,
        region_houm
FROM stg_demand_portalapplicant

WITH payments_cl AS (
SELECT
    movements.date::TIMESTAMP AS payment_date ,
    COALESCE((timezone( prop_mz.timezone, movements.date::TIMESTAMP)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE),movements.date::TIMESTAMP) AS payment_date_local , 
    movements.agreed_date ,
    prop_mz.geo_id  ,
    _id AS reservation_id ,
    movements.property_id ,
    movements.concept ,
    movements.type ,
    movements.person_data_sub_person_id ,
    status 
FROM {{ ref('stg_payments_cl_db_movements') }} AS movements 
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }} AS prop_mz 
    ON prop_mz.property_id = movements.property_id
WHERE TRUE 
    AND concept='RESERVATION' 
    AND type = 'INCOME'
    AND status IN ('PAID','REFUNDED') 
)

, payments_co AS (
select 
    movements.date::TIMESTAMP AS payment_date ,
    COALESCE((timezone( prop_mz.timezone, movements.date::TIMESTAMP)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE),movements.date::TIMESTAMP) AS payment_date_local , 
    movements.agreed_date ,
    prop_mz.geo_id  ,
    _id AS reservation_id ,  -- 'CO-' || _id reservation_id
    movements.property_id ,
    movements.concept ,
    movements.type ,
    movements.person_data_sub_person_id ,
    status 
FROM {{ ref('stg_payments_co_db_movements') }} AS movements 
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }} AS prop_mz  
    ON prop_mz.property_id = movements.property_id
WHERE TRUE 
    AND concept='RESERVATION' 
    AND type = 'INCOME'
    AND status IN ('PAID','REFUNDED') 
)

, payments_mx AS (
SELECT 
    movements.date::TIMESTAMP AS payment_date ,
    COALESCE((timezone( prop_mz.timezone, movements.date::TIMESTAMP)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE),movements.date::TIMESTAMP) AS payment_date_local , 
    movements.agreed_date ,
    prop_mz.geo_id  ,
    _id AS reservation_id ,  -- 'MX-' || _id reservation_id
    movements.property_id ,
    movements.concept ,
    movements.type ,
    movements.person_data_sub_person_id ,
    status 
FROM {{ ref('stg_payments_mx_db_movements') }} AS movements 
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }} AS prop_mz
    ON prop_mz.property_id = movements.property_id
WHERE TRUE 
    AND concept='RESERVATION' 
    AND type = 'INCOME'
    AND status IN ('PAID','REFUNDED')    
)

FROM payments_cl

    * 
FROM payments_co
UNION ALL

    * 
FROM payments_mx
)

Select
    schedules.id        schedule_id 
    , prop_mz.geo_id
    , (timezone( prop_mz.timezone, schedules.created_at)::timestamp with time zone)::date created_at
    , (timezone( prop_mz.timezone, schedules.begin_date)::timestamp with time zone)::date begin_date
    , (timezone( prop_mz.timezone, schedules.end_date)::timestamp with time zone)::date end_date
    , (timezone( prop_mz.timezone, schedules.updated_at)::timestamp with time zone)::date updated_at
    , schedules.prop_id property_id 
    , properties.supply_source
    , properties.supply_relation
    , schedules.status
    , schedules.origin
    , scheduler_scheduletypes.name as schedule_type_name
    , scheduler_appraisers.roles
    , scheduler_appraisers.email as appraiser_email
    , applicant.email --as applicant_email
    , applicant.id as  applicant_id 
from {{ ref('stg_scheduler_schedules') }} AS schedules
    left join {{ ref('stg_scheduler_scheduletypes') }} AS scheduler_scheduletypes on scheduler_scheduletypes.id  = schedules.schedule_type_id
    left join {{ ref('stg_scheduler_schedulehasapplicant') }} AS scheduler_schedulehasapplicant  on scheduler_schedulehasapplicant.schedule_id     = schedules.id 
    left join {{ ref('stg_arriendoasegurado_applicant') }} AS applicant on applicant.id = scheduler_schedulehasapplicant.applicant_id
    left join {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }} AS prop_mz  on prop_mz.property_id = schedules.prop_id 
    left join {{ ref('proc_properties') }} AS properties on properties.id = schedules.prop_id
    left join {{ ref('stg_scheduler_appraisers')}} AS scheduler_appraisers on scheduler_appraisers.id = schedules.appraiser_id
where scheduler_scheduletypes.name in ('Visit','SalesVisit')

model.houm.proc_demand_schedules_timing.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH 
relevant_events AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM {{ ref('proc_demand_schedules_appraiserevent') }} AS proc_demand_schedules_appraiserevent
)

, schedules_time AS (
    SELECT 
        id schedule_id,
        created_at,
        begin_date,
        end_date,
        updated_at
    FROM {{ ref('stg_scheduler_schedules')}}
)
-- modificar en un futuro, ideal utilizar proc_demand_schedules, pero no tiene timestamp de fecha

, max_event AS (
    SELECT 
    a.*
    FROM relevant_events AS a    
    INNER JOIN 
          (SELECT 
           schedule_id,
           action,
           MAX(created_at) AS created_at
           FROM relevant_events 
           GROUP BY 1,2    
          ) AS b 
        ON a.schedule_id = b.schedule_id
            AND a.action = b.action 
            AND a.created_at = b.created_at
)


, arrived_event AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM max_event 
    WHERE action = 'Arrived'
)

, start_event AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM max_event 
    WHERE action = 'Started'
)

, done_event AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM max_event
    WHERE action = 'Done'
)

, schedules AS (
    SELECT 
        proc_demand_schedules.schedule_id,
        proc_demand_schedules.property_id,
        dim_macrozones.country,
        dim_macrozones.geo_id,
        proc_propertydetails.latitud,
        proc_propertydetails.longitud,
        schedules_time.created_at,
        schedules_time.begin_date,
        schedules_time.end_date,
        schedules_time.updated_at,
        proc_demand_schedules.status,
        scheduler_appraisers.name,
        proc_demand_schedules.roles, 
        proc_demand_schedules.schedule_type_name,
        CASE WHEN proc_demand_schedules.email LIKE '%test.test%'
             OR proc_demand_schedules.email LIKE '%test.com%'
             OR proc_demand_schedules.applicant_id IS NULL 
             OR scheduler_appraisers.email in 
             ('oliver.houmtest@gmail.com',
              'nadiana.cazorla@houm.com',
              'ivan.santibanez@houm.com',
              'luis.montecinos@houm.com',
              'evelyn.gonzalez@houm.com',
              'houmer_cl@houm.com',
              'ivan.cerda@houm.com',
              'alejandra.ramirez@houm.com',
              'manuel.duran@houm.com',
              'eyal.levy@houm.com',
              'antoni.fuenmayor@houm.com',
              'sonia.alvarado@houm.com') THEN TRUE
             ELSE FALSE 
             END AS is_test,
        CASE WHEN scheduler_appraisers.roles::text LIKE '%Dummy%' THEN TRUE 
             ELSE FALSE 
             END AS is_dummy   
    FROM {{ ref('proc_demand_schedules') }} proc_demand_schedules
    LEFT JOIN schedules_time 
       ON schedules_time.schedule_id = proc_demand_schedules.schedule_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_propertydetails') }} proc_propertydetails
       ON proc_propertydetails.property_id = proc_demand_schedules.property_id 
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_scheduler_appraisers') }} scheduler_appraisers      
       ON scheduler_appraisers.email = proc_demand_schedules.appraiser_email
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }} proc_properties_mz
       ON proc_properties_mz.property_id = proc_demand_schedules.property_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('dim_macrozones') }} dim_macrozones  
       ON dim_macrozones.geo_id = proc_properties_mz.geo_id 
    WHERE TRUE
    AND proc_demand_schedules.supply_relation!='New Properties'
    AND scheduler_appraisers.roles::text NOT LIKE '%NonActive%'
    AND proc_demand_schedules.begin_date IS NOT NULL 
    AND proc_demand_schedules.created_at IS NOT NULL 
    )

SELECT 
    schedules.schedule_id,
    schedules.property_id,
    schedules.country,
    schedules.geo_id,
    schedules.latitud latitude,
    schedules.longitud longitude,
    schedules.created_at,
    schedules.begin_date,
    schedules.end_date,
    schedules.status,
    schedules.schedule_type_name,
    schedules.name houmer,
    schedules.roles,
    ST_Transform(ST_SetSRID(ST_Point(arrived_event.longitude, arrived_event.latitude), 4326), 3857) AS arrived_point,
    ST_Transform(ST_SetSRID(ST_Point(start_event.longitude,  start_event.latitude), 4326), 3857) as start_point,  
    ST_Transform(ST_SetSRID(ST_Point(done_event.longitude,  done_event.latitude), 4326), 3857) AS done_point,
    ST_Transform(ST_SetSRID(ST_Point(schedules.longitud, schedules.latitud), 4326) , 3857) AS property_point ,
    arrived_event.created_at AS arrived_date, -- fecha_llegada_visita,
    start_event.created_at AS start_date, -- fecha_inicio_visita,
    done_event.created_at AS done_date, --fecha_termino_visita
    schedules.is_dummy,
    schedules.is_test
FROM schedules 
LEFT JOIN done_event
   ON done_event.schedule_id = schedules.schedule_id
LEFT JOIN start_event
   ON start_event.schedule_id = schedules.schedule_id
LEFT JOIN  arrived_event
   ON arrived_event.schedule_id = schedules.schedule_id
ORDER BY schedules.schedule_id

, schedules_time AS (
    SELECT 
        id schedule_id,
        created_at,
        begin_date,
        end_date,
        updated_at
    FROM "houmdw_prod"."dbt_staging"."stg_scheduler_schedules"
)
-- modificar en un futuro, ideal utilizar proc_demand_schedules, pero no tiene timestamp de fecha

, max_event AS (
    SELECT 
    a.*
    FROM relevant_events AS a    
    INNER JOIN 
          (SELECT 
           schedule_id,
           action,
           MAX(created_at) AS created_at
           FROM relevant_events 
           GROUP BY 1,2    
          ) AS b 
        ON a.schedule_id = b.schedule_id
            AND a.action = b.action 
            AND a.created_at = b.created_at
)


, arrived_event AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM max_event 
    WHERE action = 'Arrived'
)

, start_event AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM max_event 
    WHERE action = 'Started'
)

, done_event AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM max_event
    WHERE action = 'Done'
)

, schedules AS (
    SELECT 
        proc_demand_schedules.schedule_id,
        proc_demand_schedules.property_id,
        dim_macrozones.country,
        dim_macrozones.geo_id,
        proc_propertydetails.latitud,
        proc_propertydetails.longitud,
        schedules_time.created_at,
        schedules_time.begin_date,
        schedules_time.end_date,
        schedules_time.updated_at,
        proc_demand_schedules.status,
        scheduler_appraisers.name,
        proc_demand_schedules.roles, 
        proc_demand_schedules.schedule_type_name,
        CASE WHEN proc_demand_schedules.email LIKE '%test.test%'
             OR proc_demand_schedules.email LIKE '%test.com%'
             OR proc_demand_schedules.applicant_id IS NULL 
             OR scheduler_appraisers.email in 
             ('oliver.houmtest@gmail.com',
              'nadiana.cazorla@houm.com',
              'ivan.santibanez@houm.com',
              'luis.montecinos@houm.com',
              'evelyn.gonzalez@houm.com',
              'houmer_cl@houm.com',
              'ivan.cerda@houm.com',
              'alejandra.ramirez@houm.com',
              'manuel.duran@houm.com',
              'eyal.levy@houm.com',
              'antoni.fuenmayor@houm.com',
              'sonia.alvarado@houm.com') THEN TRUE
             ELSE FALSE 
             END AS is_test,
        CASE WHEN scheduler_appraisers.roles::text LIKE '%Dummy%' THEN TRUE 
             ELSE FALSE 
             END AS is_dummy   
    FROM "houmdw_prod"."dbt_processing"."proc_demand_schedules" proc_demand_schedules
    LEFT JOIN schedules_time 
       ON schedules_time.schedule_id = proc_demand_schedules.schedule_id
    LEFT JOIN "houmdw_prod"."dbt_processing"."proc_propertydetails" proc_propertydetails
       ON proc_propertydetails.property_id = proc_demand_schedules.property_id 
    LEFT JOIN "houmdw_prod"."dbt_staging"."stg_scheduler_appraisers" scheduler_appraisers      
       ON scheduler_appraisers.email = proc_demand_schedules.appraiser_email
    LEFT JOIN "houmdw_prod"."dbt_processing"."proc_properties_mz" proc_properties_mz
       ON proc_properties_mz.property_id = proc_demand_schedules.property_id
    LEFT JOIN "houmdw_prod"."dbt_dims"."dim_macrozones" dim_macrozones  
       ON dim_macrozones.geo_id = proc_properties_mz.geo_id 
    WHERE TRUE
    AND proc_demand_schedules.supply_relation!='New Properties'
    AND scheduler_appraisers.roles::text NOT LIKE '%NonActive%'
    AND proc_demand_schedules.begin_date IS NOT NULL 
    AND proc_demand_schedules.created_at IS NOT NULL 
    )

SELECT 
    schedules.schedule_id,
    schedules.property_id,
    schedules.country,
    schedules.geo_id,
    schedules.latitud latitude,
    schedules.longitud longitude,
    schedules.created_at,
    schedules.begin_date,
    schedules.end_date,
    schedules.status,
    schedules.schedule_type_name,
    schedules.name houmer,
    schedules.roles,
    ST_Transform(ST_SetSRID(ST_Point(arrived_event.longitude, arrived_event.latitude), 4326), 3857) AS arrived_point,
    ST_Transform(ST_SetSRID(ST_Point(start_event.longitude,  start_event.latitude), 4326), 3857) as start_point,  
    ST_Transform(ST_SetSRID(ST_Point(done_event.longitude,  done_event.latitude), 4326), 3857) AS done_point,
    ST_Transform(ST_SetSRID(ST_Point(schedules.longitud, schedules.latitud), 4326) , 3857) AS property_point ,
    arrived_event.created_at AS arrived_date, -- fecha_llegada_visita,
    start_event.created_at AS start_date, -- fecha_inicio_visita,
    done_event.created_at AS done_date, --fecha_termino_visita
    schedules.is_dummy,
    schedules.is_test
FROM schedules 
LEFT JOIN done_event
   ON done_event.schedule_id = schedules.schedule_id
LEFT JOIN start_event
   ON start_event.schedule_id = schedules.schedule_id
LEFT JOIN  arrived_event
   ON arrived_event.schedule_id = schedules.schedule_id
ORDER BY schedules.schedule_id

model.houm.proc_demand_whatsapp.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='view') }}

WITH properties_mz AS (
    SELECT properties_mz.property_id,
           properties_mz.geo_id
    FROM {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }} AS properties_mz
)
   , city_lead AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT id                                    AS lead_id,
                    country,
                    city,
                    CASE
                        WHEN country LIKE 'cl' THEN 79::INT
                        WHEN country LIKE 'co' THEN 14::INT
                        WHEN country LIKE 'mx' THEN 19::INT
                        ELSE NULL END                     AS geo_id_country,
                    CASE
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Medell%n%' THEN 31::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Bogot%' THEN 14::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Región Metropolitana%' THEN 79::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Santiago%' THEN 79::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Valparaíso%' THEN 11::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Concepción%' THEN 8::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Bío Bío%' THEN 8::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Ciudad de México%' THEN 19::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%México%' THEN 19::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Monterrey%' THEN 54::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Nuevo Leó%' THEN 54::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%MTY%' THEN 54::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Tijuana%' THEN 67::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Guadalajara%' THEN 30::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Puebla%' THEN 19::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%Querétaro%' THEN 19::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%GDL%' THEN 30::INT
                        WHEN city LIKE '%CDMX%' THEN 19::INT
                        ELSE NULL END                     AS geo_id_city,
                    COALESCE(geo_id_city, geo_id_country) AS geo_id_lead
    FROM {{ ref('stg_demand_lead') }}
)
   , stg_demand_whatsapp AS (
    SELECT stg_demand_whatsapp.id,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.created_at,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.updated_at,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.phone,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.lead_id,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.property_id,
           properties_mz.geo_id                                       AS geo_id_property,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.business_type,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.to_number,
           CASE
               WHEN to_number LIKE '+57%' THEN 14::INT
               WHEN to_number LIKE '57%' THEN 14::INT
               WHEN to_number LIKE '+56%' THEN 79::INT
               WHEN to_number LIKE '56%' THEN 79::INT
               WHEN to_number LIKE '+52%' THEN 19::INT
               WHEN to_number LIKE '52%' THEN 19::INT END             AS geo_id_to_number,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.origin,
           CASE
               --Portales
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%MercadoLibre%' THEN 'MercadoLibre'
               WHEN origin ILIKE 'Portal Inmobiliario' THEN 'MercadoLibre'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%meli%' THEN 'MercadoLibre'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%Inmuebles24%premier%' THEN 'Inmuebles24 Premier'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%Inmuebles24%' THEN 'Inmuebles24'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%I24%' THEN 'Inmuebles24'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%yapo%' THEN 'Yapo'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%Properati%' THEN 'Proppit'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%Properaty%' THEN 'Proppit'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%Chile Propiedades%' THEN 'Chile Propiedades'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%Proppit%' THEN 'Proppit'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%ciencuadras%' THEN 'Ciencuadras'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%Metrocuadrado%' THEN 'MetroCuadrado'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%inca%aiz%' THEN 'FincaRaiz'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%Vivanuncios%' THEN 'Vivanuncios'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%GoPlaceIt%' THEN 'GoPlaceIt'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%iCasas%' THEN 'iCasas'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%lamudi%' THEN 'Lamudi'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%metroscubicos%' THEN 'MetrosCubicos'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%Segundamano%' THEN 'Segundamano'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%TocToc%' THEN 'Segundamano'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%whatsapp%' THEN 'Whatsapp Portales'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%portales%' THEN 'Whatsapp Portales'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%essa%gebird%' THEN 'MessageBird'
               --Houm
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%houm%' THEN 'Houm'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%Marketplace%' THEN 'Houm'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%Asesor%a%' THEN 'Houm'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%.%' THEN 'Whatsapp Portales'
               WHEN origin ILIKE '%property%' THEN 'Otro'
               ELSE origin
               END                                                    AS origin_clean,
           CASE
               WHEN origin_clean IN ('Yapo', 'Chile Propiedades', 'TocToc', 'Chile Propiedades') THEN 79::INT
               WHEN origin_clean IN ('Proppit', 'FincaRaiz', 'Ciencuadras', 'MetroCuadrado') THEN 14::INT
               WHEN origin_clean IN ('Segundamano', 'Inmuebles24', 'Inmuebles24 Premier', 'Lamudi', 'Vivanuncios', 'EasyBroker') THEN 19::INT
               ELSE NULL END                                          AS geo_id_portal,
           COALESCE(geo_id_property, geo_id_to_number, geo_id_portal) AS geo_id_whatsapp
    FROM {{ ref('stg_demand_whatsapp') }} AS stg_demand_whatsapp
        LEFT JOIN properties_mz 
            ON properties_mz.property_id = stg_demand_whatsapp.property_id
)
   , stg_demand_whatsapp_2 AS (
    SELECT stg_demand_whatsapp.id,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.created_at,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.updated_at,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.phone,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.lead_id,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.property_id,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.business_type,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.to_number,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.origin,
           stg_demand_whatsapp.origin_clean,
           COALESCE(geo_id_whatsapp, geo_id_lead) AS geo_id
    FROM stg_demand_whatsapp
        LEFT JOIN city_lead 
            ON stg_demand_whatsapp.lead_id = city_lead.lead_id
)
SELECT stg_demand_whatsapp_2.id,
       stg_demand_whatsapp_2.created_at,
       stg_demand_whatsapp_2.updated_at,
       stg_demand_whatsapp_2.phone,
       stg_demand_whatsapp_2.lead_id,
       stg_demand_whatsapp_2.property_id,
       stg_demand_whatsapp_2.business_type,
       stg_demand_whatsapp_2.to_number,
       stg_demand_whatsapp_2.origin,
       stg_demand_whatsapp_2.origin_clean,
       stg_demand_whatsapp_2.geo_id,
       dim_mz.country,
       dim_mz.region_houm
FROM stg_demand_whatsapp_2
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('dim_macrozones') }} AS dim_mz 
        ON stg_demand_whatsapp_2.geo_id = dim_mz.geo_id
